<COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">This month 's visit of <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Bangladesh</COREF> Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina</COREF> to Washington</COREF> is further evidence of the strengthening ties between <COREF ID="16" TYPE="IDENT"><COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">the United States</COREF> and <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Bangladesh</COREF></COREF> .
