<COREF ID="57" TYPE="IDENT">The Fund</COREF> will make it *EXP*-1 possible for <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Bangladesh</COREF> to redirect some debt repayment money to projects and at *PRO* preserving unique eco-systems and protecting the environment .
<COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">The Bangladesh government</COREF> also deserves credit for *PRO* <COREF ID="80" TYPE="IDENT">making</COREF> significant progress toward *PRO* eliminating child labor in the garment industry .
<COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">The US</COREF> is committed to *PRO*-1 working with <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Bangladesh</COREF> on <COREF ID="80" TYPE="IDENT">this</COREF> and other core labor standards including freedom of association and collective bargaining .
